e these girls.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Patricia thran","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/58720733"},{"created_at":"2014-05-01T15:40:04Z","content":"This needs to be a world wide priority!","like_count":0,"author_name":"E MacDougall","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/837621"},{"created_at":"2014-05-05T20:56:39Z","content":"These girls need to come back! This is horrible","like_count":0,"author_name":"Grace Boyd","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/71546586"},{"created_at":"2014-05-06T01:41:08Z","content":"Children need to be protected. Families need to be reunited.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lynn Ecsedy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/14817141"},{"created_at":"2014-05-05T01:13:31Z","content":"Because I am a Mother and I cannot imagine what the young ladies and families are going through.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Donna Jackson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/14056495"},{"created_at":"2014-05-06T15:40:56Z","content":"Because they deserve freedom","like_count":0,"author_name":"Zina Monteiro","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/91784545"},{"created_at":"2014-04-30T16:35:56Z","content":"Lets get these women back, now!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Barbara Carvallo","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1632641"},{"created_at":"2014-05-06T22:52:54Z","content":"This should not be.....","like_count":0,"author_name":"Donna Shanahan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/25209405"},{"created_at":"2014-05-02T01:41:13Z","content":"when will Boko Haran be held accountable for their atrocities? ","like_count":0,"author_name":"jim poole","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/91407738"},{"created_at":"2014-05-10T02:36:46Z","content":"people deserve to be treat properly not like animals or slaves","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cheryl Durant","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/31634953"},{"created_at":"2014-05-04T06:52:07Z","content":"If it was my daughter, I'd want someone to do something.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Teresa Ellis","a