as","like_count":0,"author_name":"KATHLEEN GILL","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2206827"},{"created_at":"2014-05-03T02:54:45Z","content":"Disbelief at what I have just read; how a president can sit and do nothing is despicable and abhorrent. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"LORETTA REID","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26958213"},{"created_at":"2014-05-07T00:15:34Z","content":"These 230 girls wanted to be educated, setting goals for their futures.  Who knows the type of environment they have endured over the past month.  One thing is definite though, they need to be brought to safety and be encouraged to continue pursuing their goal of an education and freedom.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Chl\u00f6e Bacon","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/6539800"},{"created_at":"2014-05-05T16:19:13Z","content":"Women are being 'downgraded' throughout the world this is just another example of the contempt that females are held in","like_count":0,"author_name":"maureen griffin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/24238421"},{"created_at":"2014-05-03T02:13:15Z","content":"Kidnapping 230?? wtf","like_count":0,"author_name":"charles diatta","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/64291023"},{"created_at":"2014-05-08T15:43:02Z","content":"Why is this important? Because human trafficing is illegal and these girls need to be returned to their families. What a dumb question....","like_count":0,"author_name":"Anne-Kristine Blake","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/340165"},{"created_at":"2014-05-08T16:23:17Z","content":"I have a daughter - if anyone were to kidnap her from anywhere, let alone a school, there would be hundreds of law enforcement professionals bearing down on our community working to get her back within 24 hours - we owe the same support to little girls all over the world. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Elizabeth Benditt","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/65878910"},{"created_at":"2014-05-06T03:05:07Z","content":"This is about human rights.","like_c